### Context

This Data Was Initially Extracted for An Project I Was Working on. Now I Making it Public, So That Many Others Can Work on It.


### Content
This Dataset of Image Consists of Images of All 809 Pokemons and Their Mega Evolution and Alolan Forms. The Images are Titled According to Theiir Pokedex Index Number. Image Sizes are 475x475 pixels


### Acknowledgements

This Data is Extracted From Various Sites Like, pokemondb.net and pokemon.com
